com.fasterxml.jackson.databind.deser.ContextualDeserializer, com.fasterxml.jackson.databind.deser.NullValueProvider, Serializable
public class CustomInstantDeserializer<T extends org.threeten.bp.temporal.Temporal> extends com.fasterxml.jackson.datatype.threetenbp.deser.ThreeTenDateTimeDeserializerBase<T>
Deserializer for ThreeTen temporal Instants, OffsetDateTime, and ZonedDateTimes. Adapted from the jackson threetenbp InstantDeserializer to add support for deserializing rfc822 format.
Author:
Nick Williams
